  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So there was a [? carbide ?] lamp, which was, you know-- it had a-- a certain-- that was on-- a certain-- I can't describe to you.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it was an artific-- made an artificial light-- very strong.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was very, very bad for the eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my eyes are not good at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I used to do embroidery and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Met a charming family called, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Kosheva. ?] They was-- he was a professor of the-- he invented the first Polish alphabet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they befriended-- I befriended them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They befriended me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the daughter was getting married to a sort of nobleman, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They asked me to move to their place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I made the whole trousseau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I never-- I made fur coats, and a wedding dress, and everything possible you can imagine I made for them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And earned-- whatever I earned went straight to [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Kerschnerski's ?] family-- coal, and food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so I really supported them during this time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was staying-- I was staying with them for about-- for about [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Jew-- it was at a certain time, one night-- it was early morning, maybe five o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The German police, you know, with that car, with the noise, with the uniform, with the-- with the rifles, with the helmets, arrived in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened was, at some point, two couples arrived in the Zielonka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One lived next door to our-- it was like a little-- lived like, in in a wooden-- wooden villa, and opposite, another couple.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were very friend-- good friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was in the attic there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I looked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Germans took the couple from that, straight away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as they were taking them out, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
